Great time in Tennessee fishing in the Kayak Fishing World Championship with @teamusakayak 💪 Fishing was tough and just getting a limit of 5 was a huge accomplishment. I ended up 5th overall and Team USA took the Gold. The scoring format forced everyone on the  team to do well in order to win and we did just that 🤩 Thanks to Team USA organizers and my teammates. I hope to participate again in the future. #kayakfishing @dakota.lithium @hobieeyewear @hobiefishing @crowderrods @doafishinglures @yozuri_lures @froggtoggs @southriveroutfitters @catchfishingtackle

2023 Red Snapper trip was a weather circus, but we made it work. Only got to get out 2 out of the 4 days. Each trip was a rush to just get out and snag two and come back before next storm came through. Still grabbed some studs. Might have to come back for late season. #kayakfishing #snapper @hobieeyewear @crowderrods @southriveroutfitters @catchfishingtackle
